    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      288.26,
      545.69,
      319.88
    ],
    "text": "Former Media Secretary Arrested Over Alleged Criminal Misappropriation of State Property \u2013 Financial Crimes Investigation Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      334.36,
      557.4,
      375.24
    ],
    "text": "On 05.06.2026, officers of the Financial Crimes Investigation Division of the Criminal Investigation Department arrested a former media secretary to a former minister in connection with an investigation into the alleged criminal misappropriation of state property.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      389.68,
      534.13,
      430.58
    ],
    "text": "The suspect, a 52-year-old resident of Colombo 02, is alleged to have unlawfully utilized state resources during his tenure as Media Secretary to the former Ministry of Services and Common Amenities.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      445.14,
      556.33,
      499.82
    ],
    "text": "Investigations have revealed that the suspect allegedly violated the provisions of the Public Property Act by misappropriating state funds amounting to Rs. 1,746,000 (Rupees One Million Seven Hundred and Forty-Six Thousand). The alleged offence involved the unauthorized use of vehicles hired for the operational activities of the State Engineering Corporation for media-related purposes.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      514.38,
      540.48,
      541.46
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being carried out by the Financial Crimes Investigation Division of the Criminal Investigation Department.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
